mixin faq
  style.
    body {
        margin: 0; /* Hapus margin di body */
        padding: 0; /* Hapus padding di body */
    }
    .content {
        padding: 50px; 
        margin: 0; /* Hapus margin untuk mengisi ruang secara penuh */
        color: white;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 5em; /* Mengatur ukuran font untuk h1 */
        color: white; /* Mengubah warna teks menjadi putih */
        margin: 0; /* Hapus margin untuk h1 */
        padding: 20px 0; /* Tambahkan padding atas dan bawah */
        text-align: center; /* Mengatur teks agar rata kanan */
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 2em; /* Ukuran font untuk h2 */
        color: white; /* Mengubah warna teks menjadi putih */
        margin: 20px 0; /* Margin atas dan bawah untuk h2 */
    }
    p {
        font-size: 1.5em; /* Ukuran font untuk p */
        color: white; /* Mengubah warna teks menjadi putih */
        margin: 10px 0; /* Margin atas dan bawah untuk p */
        padding: 0; /* Hapus padding untuk p */
    }

  .content
    h1 FAQ

    h2 1. What is The Cartel Marketplace?
    p The Cartel Marketplace is an online platform that connects buyers and sellers for a wide 
    p range of quality products, from fashion to electronics, offering the best deals and a
    p seamless shopping experience.

    h2 2. How do I register on The Cartel?
    p To register, visit our registration page and fill out the required information. You will receive a
    p confirmation email once your registration is successful.

    h2 3. What payment methods are accepted?
    p We accept various payment methods, including credit cards, bank transfers, and e-wallets. 
    p Please choose the method that suits you best during checkout.

    h2 4. How can I return a product?
    p If you are not satisfied with the product you received, you can request a return within 14 
    p days of receiving the item. Please ensure the product is in its original condition and 
    p complete.
